options right now, but remember: Foliage with vibrant color can be
had with trees, shrubs, perennials or annuals _ some that bloom,
some that don't. The challenge is combining those plants so that
their foliage complements each other. Our foliage guide shows how
to mix and match plants for maximum color. (Flanders, Atlanta
