<P>
   &UR; COLUMNS: &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   MASTER-CHEF (New York) _ The column: Cod with mashed potatoes;
with recipe.
</P>
<P>
   SIMPLE-COOKING (Undated) _ The column: Risotto-style pasta with
asparagus; with recipe. By Mark Bittman.
</P>
<P>
   WINETALK (Undated) _ The weekly wine column: Dueling merlots: a
wine that's a great idea in France, one step up from watery
cabernet in California. By Frank J. Prial.
</P>
<P>
   With Photo.
</P>
<P>
   TASTINGS (Undated) _ The column: Sardinian reds. By Eric Asimov.
