<HEADLINE>
RED KEN RISING 
</HEADLINE>
   ATTENTION EDITORS: The following excellent ``separate-buy'' article
about Ken Livingstone, who is likely to be London's next mayor, is
from The New York Times Magazine. It can be purchased _ the rate is
not prohibitive _ by contacting one of the following New York Times
Syndicate sales representatives:  
