<TEXT>
<P>
   Sports stories from The New York Times News Service for
WEDNESDAY, April 19.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-VECSEY-COLUMN (Undated) _ Sports column on the early-season
injuries and controversies plaguing the Mets. By George Vecsey.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-METS-BREWERS (New York) _ Milwaukee at Mets, 7 p.m. By Tyler
