<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    POLITICAL PLATFORMS BECOMING INTERACTIVE AFFAIRS
 &HT;    Eds: Corrects quote in 3rd graf to ``allows you to craft.''
 &HT;    360&AMP;add. Moving in the (w) Washington and (p) political
categories.
