gas mileage. Just like a diet, don't expect to see huge immediate
results, but consider the gain over a month or six weeks. It will
add up to a tank of gas, more or less. (Sharp, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). Includes 1-column color photograph of
columnist.
</P>
