   TECHNOCAR _ Car commercials. They use really cool, techno music
in the ads. Nissan's got a cool commercial with techno music;
Volkswagen is a wonderful repeat offender. (Hutchins, Palm Beach
Post). WITH PHOTOS. MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   AVANTI _ VILLA RICA, Ga. _ Few cars have captured aficionados'
attention like the Studebaker Avanti. And few cars have shown the
Avanti's catlike ability to survive. Studebaker may be long gone as
an automaker, but the latest edition of the Avanti is taking shape
in a converted hosiery mill in Villa Rica under the guidance of
former Avanti consultant, sales representative and collector John
Seaton. (Ritzler, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
