<SLUG> BC-RAC-STEWARDS-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
STEWARDS USE VARIOUS TOOLS TO MAKE THE CORRECT CALLS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TIM PRICE 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
